{"tid":2029974,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★國安法消息影響   Google「移民」「台灣」搜尋量暴增 4 倍","createTime":"2020-05-22T13:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-22T14:10:36.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"810babf33f018b27bc1e29162854919751dc2718","tid":2029974,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:28:46.000Z","msg":"中國政府昨日（21日）公佈全國人大會議議程，計劃頒布一項新的國家安全法，建立香港特區維護國家安全法律制度。消息一出，「移民」、「台灣」等關鍵字成香港 Google 搜尋熱門字眼，搜尋數量在昨晚暴增至平日的 4 倍以上。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n據 Google Trends 資料顯示，在昨晚人大宣布將訂立「港版國安法」後，「移民」以及「台灣」等字眼瞬間上升，而與「移民」有關的字眼亦變成香港地區的 Google 搜尋關鍵字，搜尋次數暴增到原本的 4 倍以上，而「移民 台灣」的搜尋熱度更暴升 10 倍。<br />\n<br />\n <a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/22/google-taiwan-immigration/google/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F22%2Fgoogle-taiwan-immigration%2Fgoogle%2F&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSkzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=88b384da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/22/google-taiwan-immigration/google/</a>"},{"pid":"381d146ea4e94da3337f09602e12aaac872afe27","tid":2029974,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8091e6fd5a8ed43239170ff4e6a4350f1a9fa9","tid":2029974,"uid":335303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"r